Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
The audio version of everyone's favorite animated podcast!

To fix the future, we must turn to the youth! But maybe not these guys. With little knowledge and no research, comedians Willie Simon and Eric Freedman irreverently tackle the issues of today without ever having a chance of solving them. Just like everyone else. They can’t even walk yet and they’re already running their mouths.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
